sentence: Looking at options trading activity among components of the S&P 500 index, there is noteworthy activity today in T-Mobile US Inc (Symbol: TMUS), where a total volume of 25,751 contracts has been traded thus far today, a contract volume which is representative of approximately 2.6 million underlying shares (given that every 1 contract represents 100 underlying shares).
That number works out to 102.1% of TMUS's average daily trading volume over the past month, of 2.5 million shares.
Particularly high volume was seen for the $85 strike call option expiring March 20, 2020, with 19,793 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 2.0 million underlying shares of TMUS.
